subject: Diving (Sports Event)
Diving and Divers
Swimming
lead_paragraph: The Moose Moss Aquatic Center in Moultrie, Ga., a Deep South farm town, is home to the Moss Farms Diving Tigers -- perhaps the country's most improbable diving powerhouse.
